is bring Tom back.

01:08:32.640 --> 01:08:36.399
I'm Reg Keys, father of Tom Keys,
murdered in Iraq,

01:08:36.439 --> 01:08:38.399
and, without that,
what good am I to you?

01:08:48.040 --> 01:08:49.040
I predicted this.

01:08:50.399 --> 01:08:53.560
I said, halfway through
