01:09:05.120 --> 01:09:06.240
Sally?

01:09:07.760 --> 01:09:08.880
Yes?

01:09:10.399 --> 01:09:11.479
What do you think?

01:09:14.720 --> 01:09:15.800
Please?

01:09:18.359 --> 01:09:20.520
