or swallowing pills,

01:10:16.480 --> 01:10:19.440
then I'm hoovering,
polishing, scrubbing...

01:10:22.960 --> 01:10:24.920
..and I forget precisely nothing.

01:10:28.440 --> 01:10:29.440
But his mum...

01:10:31.080 --> 01:10:32.080
..everything.

01:10:33.600 --> 01:10:35.600
Hours, days, everything.

01:10:38.400 --> 01:10:41.680
And, vicious bitch that I am,

01:10:41.720 --> 01:10:45.800
I start reminding her
that he's dead.

01:10:49.960 --> 01:10:52.680
"He's dead, you stupid woman.

