01:11:29.480 --> 01:11:31.520
Just go back to Sedgefield, really.

01:11:42.960 --> 01:11:44.000
Richard?

01:11:48.160 --> 01:11:49.760
I want you to go back too, Dad.

01:11:51.320 --> 01:11:52.400
It's an adventure.

01:11:54.400 --> 01:11:56.920
And I know Tom's
been killed and that,

01:11:56.960 --> 01:12:01.160
